libpca
------------------------------------------
libpca is a C++ library for principal component analysis and related
transformations.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libarmadillo15-15.2.6-1bl1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libpca-devel-1.3.4-1bl2
  libpca1-1.3.4-1bl2
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-15-3
  autoconf-archive-2024.10.16-1
  automake-20250528-1
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libarmadillo-devel-15.2.6-1bl1
  libtool-2.5.4-1
  make-4.4.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/bloomen/libpca

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/bloomen/libpca/archive/refs/tags/1.3.4.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libpca-1.3.4-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libpca-1.3.4-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libpca-1.3.4-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libpca-1.3.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libpca1-1.3.4-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libpca-devel-1.3.4-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libpca)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libpca.README
  /usr/share/doc/libpca/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libpca/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libpca/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libpca/README.md

(libpca1)
  /usr/bin/cygpca-1.dll

(libpca-devel)
  /usr/include/pca.h
  /usr/lib/libpca.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libpca.pc

